creator: StrikeTec
descriptionHtml:
StrikeTec is the ultimate boxing workout for men and women who want to burn fat, lose weight, boost energy, and increase stamina the fun way. StrikeTec boxing technology delivers metrics that matter, helping you achieve measurable results and improve performance.

No experience required! StrikeTec contains boxing combo workouts for beginner, intermediate, and advanced levels. Free app download allows you to create a profile and get access to all features excluding the training screens (which require StrikeTec sensors, sold separately).

Videos & Guided Training

Learn everything from throwing that first punch to the most complex techniques with our follow-along instructional videos. The app currently has 5 video categories:
Basics: basic moves, punch types, beginner tips
Combos: For daily workouts, learn and master different combinations at your own pace
Set Routines: Choose your skill level, get real-time feedback as you track every punch
Boxing Workouts: For those ready to sweat, full-length workouts with coaching tips and analytics
Data Science: StrikeTec founder & CEO Wes Elliott takes you behind the scenes to show you the physics and how the app interprets data.

Workouts from the pros! StrikeTec instructors have years of training and experience and will show you how to reach your true potential.

StrikeTec Sensors

For the full experience, connect with StrikeTec sensors which are discreetly secured to the wrist. They measure:
Speed
Power
Endurance (Punches Per Minute)
Punch Count
Punch Technique
Performance Ranking (Bad, Average, Excellent) for each metric
Punch Reach
Reaction Time

StrikeTec app analyzes the data and displays the info in an easy-to-understand graph.
We’ll show you what you are doing wrong and how to fix it: Correct and Incorrect punch feedback during combo and set training.

Training Tools

StrikeTec offers a variety of training modes for different levels and activities. Live data as you punch as well as detailed session results for review:
Performance History: measure improvement over time, find peak workout. View progress & totals, or breakdowns of individual sessions, specific time-frames.
The Training Zone: Train on your own with the boxing timer or detailed power & speed graphs. Every punch is calculated and recorded.
Goals: create milestones to keep motivated. Short term, long term, casual, or ambitious.
Schedules: Don’t procrastinate, reminders will keep you working out and routines organized.
Skills Challenges: Focus on one particular metric: speed, power, reaction time or endurance.

Socialize, Compare, & Compete

Motivate gym buddies, make new friends. Work together and challenge each other for fun and fitness.

My Public Profile: Choose to show your training data, stats, & achievements. Profile photos are linked from Facebook. (optional)
Public Leaderboard shows all StrikeTec members who want to share their data. Earn points through participation, progress, and amazing scores. You can also view skill-specific boards for speed, power, & endurance.
Challenge any StrikeTec member to a fight. Want to really get competitive? Post wins & losses to the leaderboard.
Follow any member, even pros, to see their stats.
Chat privately with connections in our messaging app.

Features for Coaches
COMING SOON
